      "text": "1. 将{messages} 每个条目写入本地文件中，进行持久化存储",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. 将{messages} 每个条目写入本地文件中，进行持久化存储",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "jKYkOqNP-KrjjqUtBP2yC",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1292.7307477320444,
      "y": 987.355935451417,
      "width": 636.69970703125,
      "height": 350,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ae",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 554156505,
      "version": 323,
      "versionNonce": 1661530777,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "2Q1jWd3HM4zYL_9rNE9Ua",
          "type": "arrow"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1778831141247,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2. 将{messages} 进行JSON.stringfy(), 并且截取前80000个字符赋给\n变量 conversation\n\n3. 组合压缩上下文prompt\n`Summarize this coding-agent conversation so work can continue.\nPreserve:\n1. The current goal\n2. Important findings and decisions\n3. Files read or changed\n4. Remaining work\n5. User constraints and preferences\nBe compact but concrete.\n\n${conversation}`;",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2. 将{messages} 进行JSON.stringfy(), 并且截取前80000个字符赋给\n变量 conversation\n\n3. 组合压缩上下文prompt\n`Summarize this coding-agent conversation so work can continue.\nPreserve:\n1. The current goal\n2. Important findings and decisions\n3. Files read or changed\n4. Remaining work\n5. User constraints and preferences\nBe compact but concrete.\n\n${conversation}`;",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
